class:: GLPlayImg
summary:: display an image loaded on the server.
related:: Classes/GLPlayVid, Classes/GLShowImgTex, Classes/GLShowVidTex
categories:: UGens>Video


Description::

Displays an image loaded on the server represented by an image ID.


classmethods::

method::fr

argument::imgID
The image with this ID is displayed.


Examples::

code::

// load an image on the server and display it
(
~imgID = 0;
GLImage.new(~imgID, "/path/to/image.jpg");

{ GLPlayImg.fr(~imgID) }.play;
)

::
